'''Dr. Dave''' is a therapist at Pacific Serenity Treatment Center.

==History==
Dr. Dave did group therapy sessions with [[Amelia Shepherd]] and [[Hailey]] at Pacific Serenity Treatment Center. He later also facilitated a session between Amelia and her friends as she tried to make amends with them.

==Career==
He is a therapist at Pacific Serenity Treatment Center.
